text: Straßburger Straße is an underground rapid transit station located in the Hamburg district of Dulsberg, Germany. The station was opened in 1963 and is served by Hamburg U-Bahn line U1. == Service == === Trains === Straßburger Straße is served by Hamburg U-Bahn line U1; departures are every 5 minutes. The travel time to Hamburg Hauptbahnhof takes about 13 minutes. ==Gallery== File:U-Bahnhof Straßburger Straße Eingang.jpg|One of the station's entrances == See also == * List of Hamburg U-Bahn stations ==References== == External links == * Line and route network plans at hvv.de Category:Hamburg U-Bahn stations in Hamburg Category:Buildings and structures in Hamburg-Nord Category:Railway stations in Germany opened in 1963 Category:1963 establishments in West Germany
